snippet.title: Modi Govt Asks NABARD to Disburse Rs 21K Crore to Farmers

localized.description:
Modi government asks National Bank for Agriculture and Rural Development (Nabard) to disburse Rs 21K crore to farmers. Farmers are worst affected due to demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes.
